comments: Dr. Amadeo is a great professor, very friendly, and definitely helpful. She really makes an effort to make class/lectures interesting and the workload isn\'t bad either.

Really easy class, she puts all of the PowerPoints online. There r 3 2-4 pg papers. Group presentation, midterm, and final. Expect an A. Don\'t buy the book. You will be asked to read from it a few times but it\'s not necessary at all. U won\'t be testes on book material
So nice and helpful! Great teacher!
